author: Justin Hoyo
text:
GREAT AF outlet and conveniently location near Lorong Chuan MRT! Gym is spacious, has a good variety of equipment, and their changing room area is very nice! Not the cleanest and well-maintained gym, but still acceptable! :)

Visited this gym on the weekends and it was not super crowded (not sure how‚Äôs the crowd on the weekdays though). Overall it‚Äôs a pretty decent gym with good equipment and spacious setting.. :)

author: Deviga Premmananth
text: This is a great gym to work out at! The staff is friendly, the equipment is well-maintained and clean, and the environment is welcoming. Club Manager Ann is especially friendly and approachable. I‚Äôve been coming to this gym for about two years now, and I just enrolled my son as well!

author: Aida D
text:
Just like recent reviews have mentioned, the state of the gym has changed since the change in management (I think around 3-4 months back or earlier?)

It is now:
- lacking friendly staff
- stale-smelling
- no longer clean
- no longer neat and tidy

It is quite sad, as I moved to this gym from AF NEX because it used to be clean and had a welcoming feel. The staff back then were so friendly, went the extra mile to ensure the gym ran well and were just sincere about their job.

Unless something is done about it, I am quite sure the state of the gym will continue to deteriorate.

author: yusin sim
text:
Great environment with well maintained machines also spacious gym , lesser crowd during the afternoon period , and loves the cardio studio !! Best mirror for taking selfie at the studio
Thanks to the great friendly team lead by the manager Ann

author: joanne low
text:
Amazing service by Ann the club manager - wanted to surprise my boyfriend with a one month membership and she helped so much by complementing it with the gift pack (towel, shaker bottle, massage gun)

Very friendly and took us both around to see the facilities available ! ü•∞

author: zarrin azmi
text: Great gym! The facilities are top-notch, with a wide range of equipment catering to all fitness levels. The staff are friendly and knowledgeable, always ready to offer guidance and support. The classes are motivating and varied, making it easy to stay engaged and reach your fitness goals. Overall, a fantastic place to work out and improve your health!

author: Deb Ling
text:
Nice, clean, great gym. Easily accessible, near the mrt. Decent equipment, most look relatively new. Chill staff and people. No weird smells (usually). The changing room is bright and clean.

Minor downside is that it gets crowded after 6pm and some of the dumbells are a bit rusty. Showers usually smell a bit funky.

Overall, all things considered, still really good though.

author: Kristy Lim
text: I have been here for a year. I really enjoying coming here early morning to gym before work. Meeting the same routine of ppl gym together feels like home. Manager here, and the staffs here, have become friends to me ‚ù§Ô∏è There are plenty equipments to do whole muscle groups. Yoga and workout mats have been differentiated which is really good options too! Love this gym.

author: jack
text:
gym is getting from bad to worst. disappointing.

perfect to study in, feels like a library. music is almost non existent.

gym has a sauna.
aircon not even cooling. hotter than the main shopping building. apparently, same central aircon but hot. management don't seem to find the problem as it's been like that for a few weeks already. also, they do not switch on the air con within the gym by the way.
because of that plenty of oil patches from gym users left on the bench.

gym floors and mirrors are filthy.
equipments not maintained. faulty machines not serviced for several months.
benches not maintained. they are just tapped over with duct tape.
water cooler dispenses room temp water.
changing area is smelly.
equipment is not wiped down nor are the floors cleaned.

author: T J
text:
An Outrageous Cash Grab

The new management's actions are more than a "joke"‚Äîthey're a downright insult. They've shamelessly introduced a predatory policy, charging a $10 fee just to issue a receipt, a basic document that should be provided free of charge. This is a transparent attempt to wring every last cent out of their members, especially those who, like you, have been loyal for years.

After spending at least 2-3K with the club over the last 2 years, you were are with a wall of silence. You were forced to chase them relentlessly‚Äîthrough unanswered calls, ignored emails, and unmonitored WhatsApp chats‚Äîjust to get a simple reply. And when they finally deigned to respond, they had the audacity to demand a fee for a service that costs them virtually nothing.

The justification for this extortion is as laughable as it is enraging. They claim that since they're not GST-registered, they aren't required to issue a receipt‚Äîas if a bank statement is a suitable substitute for a multi-thousand-dollar transaction. They're deliberately creating a bureaucratic nightmare, hiding behind flimsy excuses like "a lot of administration work," when they've already confirmed they have all the transaction details on hand.

This is a new low. They know that many of their members need these receipts for corporate benefits, and they're exploiting that necessity for their own gain. This isn't just about a measly $10; it's about a complete disregard for their members and a cynical ploy to profit off of their own inefficiency. It leaves a bitter taste in your mouth to see a company stoop to such a vile level.

author: Naim Ameer
text: Anytime Fitness at New Tech Park is fantastic! The place is always clean, there's plenty of equipment, and the staff are super friendly. They've really turned from strangers to friends. Sufi, Kak Ann, Maple and Dee is really friendly. Highly recommend!

author: Sihan Goi
text: Very good gym. It's new, it's clean, it's not packed, it's not huge but rather spacious, and it has pretty much all the equipment I need. 1 Hammer Strength small platform (good for deadlifts/snatches but probably not so much for split jerks), 1 Hammer Strength power rack, 1 Hammer Strength squat rack, 1 Movement First barbell (1 side makes a noise when you spin it, but works fine), 1 unmarked (Ziva?) barbell (it spins so all good), and the highlight for me is the 1 Eleiko WL bar. There are also Hammer Strength coloured bumpers from 5-25kg. No toilets here (only shower and changing rooms), and the lockers are a tad small for larger duffle bags, but other than that, no complaints!

author: VIctor Gidlevich
text:
Used to be 5 stars gym but things changed with new management few weeks ago..

*you can't use the body analyser, if you wish to do so you have to pay $10 and can only do it with personal trainer which they currently don't have..

*they trying to cut cost so they won't turn on their aircons and relying on the mall aircon. It gets really hot.. They only agree to on it during peak hours..

*staff not as friendly as the staff under previous management.

*they new cleaning guy is good üëçüèª

Overall feels like there's no management and they just have someone to pass time at the counter..

author: Rebecca Sim
text: I‚Äôve been coming to this AF for awhile now and I can say it is truly the branch that I enjoy the most. The gym is always nice smelling, clean, and also has a great amount of sunlight streaming in with huge mirrors all across which is so important. It is also always so nice that the manager, Ann, remembers my name and always greets me with a smile and help with whatever I need. All of this makes coming to the gym such a great experience!

author: Tri Ariyani
text: The gym is very clean. A good place to workout and very friendly staff. And thanks for the team Ann as club manager and Yuz as a personal coach that helps me to workout towards my goal.

author: kiankus
text: Ever since change of management. Machines that are broken are not repaired. Fitness areas are not mopped. Lockers are broken.

author: Dhinesh Sam
text: Love this place! Well maintained facility and equipment, amazing and friendly staff. I'm an introvert and I usually like to limit my interactions with people and keep to myself, but Ann and the AF NTP team have been nothing but warm and welcoming towards me, and never fail to make me feel at ease (even if it's a simple smile or a nod or a "enjoy your workout!").

author: Kimberly Wong
text: Really love the free classes here. This gym is super clean and well maintained. Love the friendly staff here too! The manager Ann is great! She always checks in to make sure we can get the class slots we want, and makes the effort to remember what the members sign up for. She‚Äôs super accommodating and goes the extra mile to build rapport with the members!

author: Neinkatz
text:
Good assortment of machines and dumbbells. Conveniently located near MRT, parking and food places at New Tech Park.
Only lacks a toilet (shower facilities are available which have a hairdryer for use too) and a landmine lever which would complement the available equipment very well.

author: Florian Parzhuber
text:
Nice Anytime Fitness. It has most of the machines you can need, including 2 power racks and a deadlift platform.

Would be nice if they could add a preacher curl machine or an EZ bar to which you can attach plates.

The toilets are located outside of the gym, which is a bit inconvenient.

They played a German HipHop radio station when I was there, which was really nice.

author: Lochana Yapa
text:
Ann, Sufi and Dee are amazing staff with great passion and dedication to the cleanliness and management of the gym. Absolutely friendly staff and will become friends eventually!

Update July 2025: New management is totally different and does not upkeep the same values and practices as old team. To those looking for a friendly gym that is also well maintained , this is not really the place to come to anymore.

author: Peggy Tan
text:
Anytime Fitness NTP is an amazing gym with a welcoming and positive atmosphere! The facilities are clean, well-maintained, and equipped with everything I need for a great workout.

A special shoutout to Manager Ann, who truly makes this place feel like home! She is incredibly friendly, always remembers our names, and greets us with a warm smile every time we step in. Her positive energy and encouragement make every visit enjoyable, and she goes the extra mile to make members feel comfortable and motivated.

If you‚Äôre looking for a gym where you feel valued and inspired, Anytime Fitness NTP is the place to be. Highly recommended! üí™üòä

author: D M
text:
I‚Äôve been a member at Anytime Fitness New Tech Park for a while now, and I can‚Äôt say enough good things about this location. The facilities are always spotlessly clean and well-maintained, creating a comfortable and welcoming environment for every workout.

A special shoutout to Ann for her outstanding service! She goes above and beyond to make everyone feel at home, always greeting members with a warm smile and positive energy. Her attention to detail and genuine care make a big difference in creating such a friendly and motivating atmosphere.

This gym is truly a great place to work out‚Äîwhether you‚Äôre just starting or looking for a regular place to train, Anytime Fitness New Tech Park has everything you need. Highly recommend!

author: Timothy Pang
text: The gym facilities and services here are clean and well maintained by Ann and her team, the staff is friendly and courteous. I have also been training with Yuz for a long period and have seen major improvement since the start, He keeps track of my routine and forms to ensure that the PT is time well spent.

author: Sean Chew
text: The staffs here are SUPER friendly, all around positive and good vibes. Equipments are well maintained as well. Ann in particular is always really friendly and greets everyone who enters and leaves the gym, love it.

author: Gary Ang
text: I would rate this a 4.2 ‚≠ê gym, it's near the MRT, parking in 1min walk away. The gym is clean. I like that they utilize the space, but because of the small space, I think equipment could have been a little bit more, they have 2 rack and 1 deadlift platform only. I like their functional area lighting. It was worth the visit.

author: aditi rungta
text:
I recently joined Anytime Fitness this month, and I couldn‚Äôt be happier with my experience so far! The gym is well-equipped, clean, and has a positive, motivating atmosphere.

A special shoutout to my personal trainer, Yuz, who has been absolutely amazing. He took the time to understand my goals and plans my workouts accordingly. His guidance, encouragement, and expertise make every session challenging yet enjoyable. I genuinely look forward to each workout. Highly recommend.

author: Aaron O
text: I feel that this gym contains all the machines and equipment i need, and is regularly cleaned and maintained. The staff are also very kind and welcoming. Also, the people are friendly and do it judge you. Overall, this gym is well maintained and i enjoy my workouts here.

author: Joseph Tan

The manager Ann is great, will be coming here more often in the future

author: Isabelle Tay
text: Anytime Fitness New Tech Park is a really great gym to work out at! The facilities are not only clean and well-maintained, but the staff are also friendly and approachable. I would really recommend checking out this gym for a welcoming and pleasant experience!

author: Alex Tan
text:
Place was clean, spacious, ample equipment, pleasant.
What I was happy with was the attitude of Club Manager, Ann. She was detailed in going thru the membership clauses and terms, membership options, and points to note. She came across as sincere and willing to listen. Thanks, Ann!

author: z q
text: Great Gym with Excellent Facilities and Friendly Staff I recently joined AFNTP and have been thoroughly impressed with my experience so far. The gym is well-maintained, and the equipment is modern and in excellent condition. There's a wide variety of machines and free weights, so whether you're into cardio, strength training, or functional fitness, there's something for everyone. The Club Manager ‚ÄòAnn‚Äô and the staff is incredibly friendly and always willing to help, whether it's with form corrections or just answering any questions I have. The gym is also very clean, with staff regularly sanitizing equipment and ensuring the locker rooms are spotless. It's clear that they prioritize cleanliness and hygiene.

author: Tricia melissa Wan
text: Love this outlet, cozy but it‚Äôs maintained really well and the staff are so friendly it always feels more inviting and less intimidating as a lady going to a public gym. Special shoutout to Ann, she‚Äôs so helpful, friendly and always has a smile on her face but u can also tell she cares a lot for the gym!

author: Meng Lay Chan

Ann the Club Manager is also very detailed and informative when it comes to explaining the gym policies and also a very engaging tour guide, she's also really friendly and welcoming ! üòä ‚Ä¶

author: ÎîîÏºÄÏù¥
text:
I strongly this NTP branch out of other Anytime facilities. Because club manager Ann is only here.
She is very kind and always take care of each member.
Also she always recommend free banana every Friday, I like it!

author: GrEaSeLiTeNiN
text: Great location, friendly staff, well lit and clean. Quite spacious except at one corner where there are two bench press/squat stations close together (which may be a little unsafe) plus a deadlift platform near to them which is also next to the barbell rack. So walking around these parts may be a bit tight. Most of the necessary equipment are there though you won't see things like a T-bar row or a preacher curl machine. Ample space at the studio section (where the punching bags are) to do warm downs and stretching. Nice corner for wash basins and shower. One suggestion is to play a better variety of TV videos.

author: Rishyam Rathakrishnan
text: the equipments in this gym is very good. the staff in these gym is very helpful and caring. the manager Ann is always cheerful and always treat everyone here very well. overall this is a good place to gym and workout.

author: Hwee Leng Siow

author: Chan Chan

author: Hamizan
text: Fantastic gym. Firstly, the staff here are very friendly and welcoming. Always get greeted by them. Feels like a second home to me.  Secondly, the cleanliness of the gym is superb, commendable job to housekeeper Sufi. Overall a wholesome gym environment.

author: Terry Lim
text: This is a very well maintained gym with high cleanliness standard. Yuz is an excellent personal trainer who will tailor the training based on the individual's goals and requirements. He is very patient and encouraging, always ensuring that the workout is effective and not prone to injury. Would highly recommend this gym and personal trainer.

author: Yue Wen Koh
text: AFNTP is a fantastic gym. Though it may not be as big and spacious as other outlets, the gym offers a wide range of machines and equipment that are always well maintained and clean. Good job to Ann and team for the good job

author: KY Lang
text: Just signed a 18 months membership with the club, the environment is clean and hygienic. Area Manager Ann is very accommodating and detailed oriented. Very thorough with the explanation as well. Looking forward to the fitness journey here with AF New Tech Park!

author: S Praema
text:
I have been with AF for about three months. I am loving this gym. It is clean, tidy & I love the fragrance. The gym is also well-equipped (not forgetting the sweets and Friday fruit day).
I am touched by the hospitality of the staffs and manager, (Kak Ann, Dee, Sufi, Maple, Herzy & Nash) as they are very friendly. Warm greetings every time we step into the gym. They are also encouraging, approachable and funny & we have become closer than friends which feels like family to me & It has become my motivation to hit the gym everyday.
Regular members here are nice and  friendly too, I highly recommend if you are unsure which gym to go!
Well done and Thank You for being awesome guys!

author: Toofat Imstuck
text: First greeted by staffs/trainers which is awesome. The space is reasonable. Cleanliness well maintained. Dumbbells always in order.

author: Alessandro P
text: Ann, Sufi, Maple. Are all the names of the wonderful staff who work at the gym. Everyone here is friendly and kind. The gym equipment here are all new and clean. Overall a lovely gym and proud to say that I go here.

author: Jonathan Williams
text:
I've been a proud member of Anytime Fitness New Tech Park for the past 2 years and I couldn't be happier with my experience. The gym has a fantastic workout atmosphere that really motivates me to push myself during my sessions.

The staff at Anytime Fitness New Tech Park are incredibly friendly and welcoming. They always greet me by name, and happy to have a chat at point of time. The staff's positive attitude is a big part of what makes this gym such a great place to work out.

The gym is equipped with a wide variety of high-quality workout machines and free weights. Whether I'm in the mood for some cardio, strength training, or functional fitness, I'm always able to find the perfect equipment to meet my needs. The equipment is well-maintained and the gym is always clean and organised.

Overall, I highly recommend Anytime Fitness New Tech Park to anyone looking for a fantastic gym experience. The great workout atmosphere, friendly staff, and excellent equipment make this one of the best fitness centers in the area. I look forward to continuing my fitness journey at Anytime Fitness New Tech Park.

author: thawda ko
text: The Gym is clean and well equipped. The NTP AF team, Ann and staff, are super friendly and enjoy working out here .Gotta enjoy complementary snack as well :)

author: Angela Tan
text: Fantastic gym that‚Äôs close to my house. Makes popping out for a workout really convenient. Echoing some of the comments - gym is really clean and well kept. Atmosphere is pleasant as well. My previous PT at this outlet Herzy - he‚Äôs really knowledgeable and friendly. Given that I‚Äôve not worked out for quite a while, he was really patient with me learning how to perform workouts and correcting posture always. Definitely set me on the right path to continue my sessions with my new PT!

author: Nur Amirah Jasman
text: AFNTP is well-maintained, clean and neat. Gym is well managed by Ann and her team. All staff on duty are always polite, friendly and approachable (: Thank you AFNTP team for always having a smile and amazing service (:

author: Benetta Chew
text: First time signing up for PT and a gym membership. 100% no regrets! Maple was very patient and encouraging from the start. She helped me change my mindset of my unhealthy fitness goals. With her guidance, she enabled me to set new sustainable goals in both food wise and exercise. In addition to that, the gym ambassadors and PTs are very lively and friendly. It makes going to the gym fun and something to look forward to after a long day at work. The gym is also well equipped such that gym goers and equipment ratio is just nice even during peak hours. A plus point is the free workshops (pilates, yoga, boxing) that this gym offers :) really encourage those who work or stay around the area to pop by to experience themselves!

author: Ong Tze Enn
text: NTP AF is clean and staff are friendly, especially Ann. She always greets members and even asks us for our feedback. Happy to have AF NTP as my home gym :)

author: NilStar789
text: New tech AF is a pretty chill place with good amount of equipment. Ann is a very sweet lady that welcomes everybody! Would visit again :)

author: Melvin Ang
text:
There are only a few factors which define the success of gyms - location, affordability, variety of equipment, cleanliness and most importantly, the trainers.

They have checked all the boxes in my opinion and kudos to the entire management and staff of Anytime Fitness. Housing a gym within a commercial space at NTP is a move worth commending and applauding. Access to a gym right below my gym certainly help to cut traveling time. I can go in, get my workout done during lunch and be back in the office to continue my day.

Coming to trainers, Nash is definitely the go-to-guy. Experienced, accommodating yet genuinely serious about ensuring his clients enjoy and benefit from his sessions. Never boring yet constantly challenging oneself to breakthrough.

author: Cindy Go go go
text: Love this gym! Great location, excellent equipment set up, hygiene and customer service. Ann was particularly helpful as she walked me through the registration process.

author: xNefarianx Lleo
text: Very nice gym that is really spacious and has all the necessary equipment! Maple was an amazing personal trainer who gave effective workouts that helped me see results, and helped me stay consistent and build confidence in going to the gym. I'd really recommend her to anyone looking for a personal trainer. She helped me a lot both physically and mentally and I am very grateful to her for that! Thank you!

author: Christie Tham
text: Was serviced by Ann, the Area Manager, during my sign up process. She was very professional and clear in explaining the terms and conditions. Gym seems to be very clean and well-kept as well.

author: Jong
text: Very friendly admin staff! Ann, the manager is very attentive and helpful! Gym is well maintained and well equipped too.

author: Delia P
text:
Have been a member of the gym for almost 2 months now and I‚Äôm really liking the atmosphere here! Everyone is really friendly, the equipment is well maintained and clean.

My personal trainer Haz who has been helping my fitness journey has been especially amazing! As I have no knowledge of how to exercise and am generally weak physically, he has been very encouraging and is knowledgeable, and makes sure I do the forms correctly to prevent injury, and provides great advice on nutrition. I‚Äôm already seeing results and feel stronger than before and more confident. I really look forward to every session! :)

author: Qaliph R
text: Clean and spacious gym with friendly and approachable staff. Putra especially is always upbeat and greeting members warmly. He assisted me in signing up for a membership plan and explained everything clearly and concisely. He‚Äôs very personable and takes the time to get to know members making the New Tech AF a more welcoming place to go to.

author: Angel Lim
text:
Been coming here for more than a year now. This AF outlet is bright and spacious with a big functional area and sufficient machines, it is clean and smells good (not sweaty or musky) (good job Sufi!), and the staff are really friendly (shoutout to Dee and Kak Ann)!

There are also group classes offered - pilates and yoga with Alice had helped build my core significantly. I also particularly enjoy my weekly PT sessions with Maple <3 and I owe much of my health, strength and physique to her!

author: Gayle Tan
text: Gym is clean and bright. Staff are friendly. Enjoying my PT sessions with Maple who is patient, encouraging and passionate in sharing her knowledgeüëçüèª ‚Ä¶

author: Ley Luvcake
text: First AF i've been to and also the outlet that got me to sign up for its membership. The staffs (Ann, Maple, Sufi, Yuz, Iman) are very friendly and approachable be it simple gesture and simple conversation. All in all, i would recommend others to sign up AF @ NTP.

author: Woohyun PARK
text: The gym is clean and new. The trainers at the gym are all very friendly. As a beginner in fitness my personal trainer(Hazzy) was very helpful. He taught lots of fitness facts like how to eat, how to train and the correct method to train so I do not injure myself. Overall this has been a great experience for me and it has given me confidence to continue on my own.

author: Victoria Tuh
text: Signed up for AF today at NTP and Ann was very helpful with bringing us through a tour of the place. The gym was very cosy and nice even during peak period.

author: oh, hi
text:
I have been a member of AF at NTP for 3 months now. The gym is quite spacious and i love the studio room. The staff is friendly as well.

I got Maple as my Personal Trainer as soon as I joined the gym. Maple is very dedicated and friendly. She pushes me to do my best in every training session. I could clearly see results only after 3,4 weeks and it has given me a lot of confidence. My strength and stamina has been improved a lot since I started. I highly recommend getting Maple as a PT if you don‚Äôt know where to start or need someone to guide you.

author: Clarine Yong
text: ATF New Tech Park is a great workout place. The staff and trainers are friendly and attentive to the needs of members. Have joined the gym for a year and engaged Maple as my personal trainer. My original plan was to try out for 6mths but decided to continue as I do see positive results from routine workout.

author: R&SH S.H
text: Love how the staffs treat you like a friend and acknowledge you by name always. Gym is clean. I got Maple as my PT and she is professional and knowledgeable and is very friendly as well.

author: Surekha Pawar
text:
I joined gym in March this year, the gym is neat and clean, thanks to housekeeper Sufi whom I always see at work.

I got Maple for my first intro PT session and I am very happy that I signed her for further sessions. Her training style is varied with functional, HIIT, strength training with progressive overload, compound movements, pyramid style etc she really keeps workout interesting and gives weekly homework as well.

She is very patient and encouraging and always answers my workout related questions with enthusiasm, which is very helpful in understanding what muscle group is being used and to make a good mind-muscle connection. I have trained previously with 3 male trainers from other gyms and even though so young she is definitely as good as them or dare I say much better.

Thanks a lot Maple for the workout guidance you provide and I hope with you I can achieve good results even though I have many health issues.

author: Joey
text: Have great service from Ann and her team.  Really enjoy coming to her gym in-charge. Very clean and well maintained.

author: Sharon Chen
text: Very new, well-equipped and clean gym. Maple is my trainer and I‚Äôm so glad I‚Äôve got her! She‚Äôs very patient and encouraging - and each session is never dull with new things to try and be challenged with. Being in the gym used to be scary for me but she has helped me built confidence with the proper techniques for. I look forward to the sessions!

author: Mahendran Chinnappa
text: Well equipped and clean gym which has the convenience of being open 24*7. I took personal training sessions with Maple , who was excellent, professional and very attentive. I believe I made good progress during the personal training sessions with her which will stand my fitness journey in good stead

author: ku dominique
text: Came back to NTP after a long time because of how great the service and equipment is. Ann was great help to me when resigning up and was very clear with all the costs

author: Victoria Tan
text:
Joined NTP's anytime fitness in June and it was easily the best decision I have made this year. The gym is clean and well-kept. I have also signed up for personal training sessions with Maple. Her workouts are effective and she is very patient and supportive. I look forward to working out every week (big step for someone who used to be quite inactive!). Highly recommended if you're looking for a personal trainer. I have seen substantial results in just a month!

Body fat: - 3.5%
Visceral fat: -21 cm^2
Muscle: +2.4 kg
Weight: +0.6kg

author: Wilbur Chia
text: always an amazing workout at AF NTP! the staff at AF NTP are really friendly and definitely add to my experience here. equipment is well maintained as well.

author: Joanne Wesbury
text:
Haz is a great personal trainer. He is very attentive while I am training, ensuring my technique is correct and that I am using the correct muscles.

He is knowledgeable and identifies areas of weakness, giving me daily stretches and exercises to do which accelerate my progress in the gym.

He is easy to chat to and discuss training goals with and has a quiet, respectful motivational technique which keep my sessions on track and successful. I'm already feeling stronger and moving better after just 3 weeks.

The gym is clean, well equipped, and provides a comfortable, friendly environment to train in. I am also loving the yoga and Pilates classes which are free for members.

author: Jemimah Yadli
text: Love the facilities and the floor space. Also great privacy! Ann is super friendly and helpful, really enjoy going to this branch.

author: Tinergy
text: Have been recommended my friend to sign up and coming to NTP fitness. It has been a great experience and always like coming to NTP. Special shoutout to Ann and her staff for always been friendly.

author: Clarence Hum
text: Great service from Ann and Team! Equipment is well maintained and hygiene is tip-top. Will recommend this AF outlet to others.

author: Justin Ho
text: Very limited machines and a lot of beginner teens with 0 gym etiquette

author: Tan Fu Nan
text: Clean and well equipped gym. Kudos to the helpful and friendly staff, Sufi and Ann for making gym-goers always feel welcome.

author: Chua Zhi Yu
text: Gym isn't too busy most of the time and quite cozy with just enough equipment for a smaller gym. Staff are very friendly especially Sufi and Ann.

author: ashvin nagi
text: Great gym to workout at, staff are extremely friendly, the gym has a great selection of equipment. They have a deadlift platform, two squat racks, one leg press, one Smith machine and a bunch of other essential machines for both upper and lower body workouts. They have a large area for yoga/streching as well. Their locker room area is always neat and their showers are always clean. I really appreciate that they have free snacks for members like bananas. This is probably the best AF I've been to.

She is truly committed to my progress. I've since felt so much more stronger, happier and a more confident version of myself. SO THANK YOU MAPLE!

text:
Just completing my annual membership with Anytime Fitness at NTP. It's a great team, with coaches and instructors who look out for you. I've worked with Herzy as my PT and he is very focused on building up strength and correcting form rather than jumping right into deadweights.

NTP is also super convenient to those in the neighbourhood while being much quieter than outlets in malls.

author: Erdinc Eroglu
text: Hazril Farris is an amazing personal trainer! Thanks to his nutrition and fitness advice, I feel like I'm taking care of myself for the first time in a long time. I've lost weight, improved my fitness, and feel much better! Because of his fun and varied routines that change on a daily basis, I've extended my workout time significantly. He is really dependable, and whenever I have asked him a question, he has always responded promptly. You will see results if you follow his advise! He is a true professional. He is always on time. He is very flexible when it comes to scheduling the next exercises.

author: Ashley Lim
text: The trainers at AF NTP have greatly aided me in my fitness journey. Special thanks to my own personal trainer, Maple, who has not only helped kickstart me into achieving my goal, but also in enjoying each individual session. Her approachability and friendliness have brought about many interesting conversations. Never would I have imagined that I could have forged such a bond with a trainer, and would highly recommend her to anyone who is thinking of joining.

- Approachable, easygoing and fun

author: Aaron Rozells
text:
Great gym with welcoming environment for both beginners and experts.

I struggled with fitness issues for some but I approached fitness trainer Maple Tan to help me on my journey. Truly dedicated to both coaching and inspiring, Maple took on the role of an amazing mentor in which not only did she coach with patience, she also gave me advice on changes I should make in terms of lifestyle and diet.

Maple is extremely willing to share her immense wealth of knowledge with her clients and never fails to wear a smile to add cheer and joy in order to make training as enjoyable as possible.

I truly recommend Maple to clients of any gender and I am extremely grateful of her training.

Here are the results I have managed to obtain with Maple in 10 sessions, which approximate to about 70 days of training:

Body fats decr. 4.1%
Visceral fat decr. 31cm2
Muscle incr. 1.5kg
Weight decr. 5.4kg

text:
My six months of training with Haz at the gym have paid off tremendously. My goal in starting to train with Haz was to increase my muscular mass. At first, I was hesitant, but now I'm pleased I made the commitment. Haz is extremely well-versed and experienced, and he takes the time to carefully consider my needs before designing a program that pushes me yet is within my capabilities. He is really encouraging and helpful, and I can always count on him to challenge me to give more than I thought I had in me.

My strength and self-assurance have increased dramatically over the past six months. I can't thank Haz enough for all his support and advice. He has been the driving force behind my physical and personal growth.

I think Haz is the best gym trainer out there and would suggest him to anybody seeking to get in shape. He is amazing.

text:
Haz has been my personal trainer for the past 8 months. With the benefit of his guidance, my physique is morphing and I now have better muscle definition and good posture.

The training regimen that Haz has devised for me is particularly suited to my body type, lifestyle and fitness goals. This personalised approach ensures that my training is focused and fruitful.

What impresses me most about Haz is his genuine commitment to ensuring that I achieve my fitness aspirations. He takes the time to check in on my progress and encourage me whenever he sees me, even outside of our training sessions.

If you are looking for a reliable, dedicated and genial personal trainer to guide you in your quest to attain your ideal physique, Haz is certainly the right man for you.
